    @ModelExternalEvents(exported={SwitchOnIndoorGarden.class,SwitchOffIndoorGarden.class,SwitchLightOnIndoorGarden.class,SwitchLightOffIndoorGarden.class})
public class IndoorGardenTestModel
extends fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.es.models.AtomicES_Model
    The class IndoorGardenTestModel implements a simple usage model that schedule events simulating the switch on, switch light on, switch light off and switch off actions on the indoor garden.

    Description

    This model is useful on for for MIL simulations. In SIL simulations, the corresponding actions are taken in software.

    White-box Invariant

     invariant       true        // no more invariant

    Black-box Invariant

     invariant       URI != null && !URI.isEmpty()
